* Iron Raptor growled and caught Senesis's fist in her hand, he would have 
to be quicker then that to get the drop on her! She then clenched her own 
fist around his and twisted cruelly, she wasn't in the mood!
Iron Raptor looked over at Plintissa for a sec and snarled to her...*

" If you can make it get onto the speeder and get the Inferno out of here! 
I'll follow after I've finished with this!"

* Iron Raptor then reaches behind her back and brings up the sword that 
Liono had given her, she always had meant to practice.
She brought the blade down hard onto Senesis's shoulder, it would obviously 
do some damage!!*
